# Class: ScoreLogger

TypeScript SDK reference

[weave](/weave/reference/typescript-sdk) / ScoreLogger ScoreLogger manages scoring for a single prediction. Returned from EvaluationLogger.logPrediction(). `Example`
    
    
    const pred = await ev.logPrediction(example, output);
    await pred.logScore("accuracy", 0.95);
    await pred.logScore("relevance", 0.8);
    await pred.finish(); // Finalizes the prediction
    

